Duties:
System Administration and installation of UNIX/LINUX/WINDOWS Servers &amp; Workstations
Software Configuration Management using Rational Clear Case and RCS
Basic Network Setup (routers, switches, IP addresses)
Database Modeling and Parameterization (Oracle)
Scripting using Java Scripts, Perl, ksh, csh, bsh, bash
Software Development using C, C++, Pascal, SQL, Java, HTML, XML, etc
Functional and Integration Testing
Site Commissioning of delivered SCADA/DMS/EMS systems
Warranty support and maintenance for delivered projects

Requirements:
Candidate must possess a Degree in Computer Science or Computer Engineering or equivalent&nbsp;
1-2 Years’ experience in SCADA/EMS/DMS systems or Real Time software development in a UNIX environment preferred though not compulsory
Independent, result-oriented and self-driven team player with good communication and problem-solving skills.
Able to handle tasks independently.
Travelling and executing of overseas project is required.
